    "rowsha": "gjXHsUx1xNEK1bXVqVpZ2XGEsdwgKq/iP4EHPSB8u9Y=",
    "originContent": "- **Android:** 10+ (Min SDK 30)",
    "translatedContent": "- **Android:** 10以上（最小SDK 30）"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "Fg42clIKe+ktauZPlveziAq2daW+WCgR8+SkkcLQWOE=",
    "originContent": "- **Root:** Required for Xposed Framework usage.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Root:** Xposed Framework使用時に必要。"
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "2/Vi5r2GLlafDlNZWH+6aX+SpVDVs6kRT+XOSSltpXA=",
    "originContent": "- **Xposed Framework:** LSPosed is recommended.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Xposed Framework:** LSPosed が推奨されます。"
  },
