  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "Qs2kz9x3hHdflUCADVazeFT5gtIzsI3LlA+gGI6QL8E=",
    "originContent": "## Installation & LSPosed Scope Configuration",
    "translatedContent": "## インストールと LSPosed のスコープ設定"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "bSOOVWQbzghKF0jbG+9/HOGQNou1wRWAZunv4i0bO9o=",
    "originContent": "1. Install the Location Joystick APK.",
    "translatedContent": "1. Location Joystick APK をインストールします。"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "UmUd8YFDpgX/neMSv/dp0yRnA5vwd1YdNlBmxjFWVFo=",
    "originContent": "2. Open your Xposed Manager (e.g. LSPosed).",
    "translatedContent": "2. Xposed マネージャー（例：LSPosed）を開きます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "V8+wBTYuHIA9x5XalVZVmheujppfHpxitizU8Dd+zCw=",
    "originContent": "3. Enable the **Location Joystick** module.",
    "translatedContent": "3. **Location Joystick** モジュールを有効にします。"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "SPLrtqOd1JNhmcloVZYqVRwJQ1fi9LCOYDqcJlxekP8=",
    "originContent": "4. **Important:** Configure the scope in LSPosed:",
    "translatedContent": "4. **重要:** LSPosed でスコープを設定します："
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "S8WCVlFFIouAiVrev4Tf+l31J3n3FVx2TPrmaVEbvG4=",
    "originContent": "    - **Android-System** (must be enabled for GNSS & system-wide mocking).",
    "translatedContent": "    - **Android-System**（GNSS とシステム全体のモックに必須）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "ic9r0p6ibOIHVMPR77gduTkhp/ul/BoYmebJ6hvjw+4=",
    "originContent": "    - **Target App(s)** (e.g. Pokémon GO, Maps).",
    "translatedContent": "    - **対象アプリ**（例：ポケモンGO、マップ）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "DgtFqn9lfZCh3G5f0mY9qvur6G70oiqEMRHMB02oA40=",
    "originContent": "5. Reboot your device (or force stop the target app and System UI if using LSPosed).",
    "translatedContent": "5. デバイスを再起動するか（LSPosed 使用時は対象アプリと System UI を強制停止してください）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "a2kFDiy3impaavt2x6jnZ3JmZU0S3iH/1qLUg0h1DUQ=",
    "originContent": "6. Open Location Joystick and grant the required permissions (Overlay, Location).",
    "translatedContent": "6. Location Joystick を開き、必要な権限（オーバーレイ、位置情報）を許可します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
